name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs

reviews.name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs
reviews.reviewText: I received this product as part of MuscleTech's testing team. I enjoyed this product and the flavored was great. The nutritional profile is amazing for a protein. I was a little thrown off by the consistency (more dense than whey protein), but it mixed great. If you're looking for an alternative to whey protein or just looking for a beef protein, give this product a shot.
reviews.title: Great Protein!

reviews.name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs
reviews.reviewText: I received a free sample as part of the muscle tech field test team and I have to admit I was a little weirded out at the thought of powdered beef. After trying it, i can definitely recommend mixing it into your daily routine. It makes me a lot less bloated than whey powder and goes down a lot easier than I expected. It doesn't taste as good as some whey, but it's a lot better than you'd expect. Try it. you'll be surprised how much you like it.
reviews.title: Less Bloat than Whey

reviews.name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs
reviews.reviewText: FInally a beef protein that isnt disgusting!! Nice job with the product profile but outstanding job on the flavoring and taste. I have tried a few other big name brands and there is no comparison in the flavor at all. I had the vanilla caramel and loved it.
reviews.title: Taste great

reviews.name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs
reviews.reviewText: I received this as part of MTs beta team. The shake mixed well with little to no clumps. To be honest though in general I don't care for Caramel flavoring and this was no different. It may be worth a try for someone who enjoys Caramel flavoring and wants something different aside from the usual Whey proteins.
reviews.title: Platinum 100% Beef Protein, Just not a Caramel Fan

reviews.name: MuscleTech Essential Series Platinum 100% Beef Protein Vanilla Caramel Dietary Supplement Powder, 2.11 lbs
reviews.reviewText: I got this as a free sample from Muscletech and was very skeptical. I have never used a beef protein before so just the name alone was throwing me off. It turned out to be great! First the nutritional information is amazing, really hard to beat in any category (fats, carb, sugar, protein) unless you hate carbs. And the taste....wow! Vanilla caramel. Yes, definitely try it out.
reviews.title: Great Flavor!
